      'art.fi.hero.h1':    'Facade Inspection in Ontario: OHSA Requirements, OBC Standards & What Owners Must Know',
      'art.fi.hero.p':     'Ontario building owners have significant facade safety obligations under OHSA, the OBC, and municipal by-laws. This guide explains the regulatory framework and what a comprehensive facade assessment involves.',
